  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Financial Consultant (No Exp / Good Benefits / Basic + Comms)",
  "description": "<p><u><strong>Roles and Responsibilities</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Develop individualised financial advice based on clients’ financial and protection needs.</li>\n  <li>Help clients with financial planning in aspects such as retirement, education and investments.</li>\n  <li>Provide clients with recommendations on wealth accumulation in accordance to their goals.</li>\n  <li>Build long-term and trusted relationships with clients.</li>\n  <li>Keep up to date with market development, investment products and other areas that can affect the market.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What We Offer:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Different proven platforms to be given to kickstart and advance in your career.</li>\n  <li>Not needed to approach own family members or friends to generate leads.</li>\n  <li>provide customizable leads platform</li>\n  <li>Provide 1 to 1 mentorship.</li>\n  <li>Extensive training provided by professional trainers to help you develop your knowledge and soft skills.</li>\n  <li>Monthly allowance and other cash incentives.</li>\n  <li>Overseas trip incentives.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><u><strong>Eligibility</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Meeting MAS-FAA regulations, you should be at least of 21 years of age to quality as a financial planner</li>\n  <li>Minimum full certificate in GCE A Level, International Baccalaureate Diploma qualification, diploma awarded by a Polytechnic in Singapore or equivalent (further specific requirements may apply to determine equivalent academic qualifications).</li>\n  <li>Good interpersonal skills.</li>\n  <li>Committed, driven and eager to succeed.</li>\n  <li>No work experience required.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><u><strong>Technical Skills and Competencies You Will Learn</strong></u></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Insurance and Financial Planning Fundamentals</li>\n  <li>Certifications in CMFAS</li>\n  <li>Communication and Networking Skills</li>\n  <li>Sales and Marketing Skills</li>\n  <li>Client Relationship Management</li>\n</ul>",
